Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:06.15,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Welcome everyone to Wednesday Downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.55,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:11.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome our first presenter, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:20.90,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Kannatsugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.27,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How unusual
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:23.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little bit weird
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He often appears in the video presentations
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I often appear in the videos in my disguise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The style he's rocking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,and the clothes are weird
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.81,0:00:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I look weird? Should I then wear some uniform?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Before presenting today's theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to ask a question to all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever done a teacher's impression
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,back when you were students?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:48.39,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think so, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.39,0:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this teacher who always spoke with her eyes half closed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.56,0:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Half closed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a classical literature teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"The novel Taketori monogatari was..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:01.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:05.24,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How can the teacher go like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If right now someone from the same high school is watching, they're probably laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.02,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If we impersonated their gestures and habits
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:14.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:17.22,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It would be hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm a professional impersonator
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I started doing impressions of my teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:23.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Your beginnings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:24.50,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and everyone laughed with them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:26.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Got you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I became a professional
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.70,0:01:29.33,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So that's how you started
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.33,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is the theory I brought to you today:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:38.71,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"If a professional impersonates real teachers, their students will die of laughter" theory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.11,0:01:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.08,0:01:47.59,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If it's already funny when a regular student does it, imagine a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.05,0:01:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to get laughs!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.99,0:01:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure about that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're professionals after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail at that, you'd become useless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:55.73,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:02:00.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Coming up next: professional impersonators try to take on teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:03.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will they get tons of laughs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:09.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also, "the stronger the tsukkomi, the funnier it gets" theory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:19.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"People won't notice if a famous song with changed lyrics is played in a store" theory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:23.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"You become powerless when holding a urine sample" theory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:45.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"If a professional impersonates real teachers, their students will die of laughter" investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.24,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Die of laughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today, we will visit Yamanashi,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,where FujiGakuen Middle School is located.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:54.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They have a class per each school year
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.02,0:02:58.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and approximately 60 students enrolled
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:59.82,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Quite cozy in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:05.76,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And these are the pros in charge of the teachers impressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:02.36,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:06.10,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That lineup is surely something!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:13.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pros visited the school in order to gather information about the teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:21.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First, when inquiring some students who already graduated:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:22.08,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this teacher, called Oomori sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomori sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomori sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his subject?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Science
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When he gets mad, he gets like super agitated
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And goes like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All they way up, suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, his intonation too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.93,0:03:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the intonation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.63,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you do an impression of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Oh my, what are you doing??"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have no heart, I'm telling you"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This might work, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always had a bad diction
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bad diction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he has a bad diction, you can't understand him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:57.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next, the pros will watch the lessons live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you understand that "other" is singular, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She raises the final "NE"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.99,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She suddenly raises the final NE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.79,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The NE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As if she were following a rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, a rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.43,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His diction is unique
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.96,0:04:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at the chalk
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:17.04,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This can be funny
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be possible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:22.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then, regarding Oomori sensei:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can exaggerate this a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.91,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I see now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.75,0:04:33.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now, Mr. "Slipping Glasses & Bad Diction" Oomori
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:37.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Has been chosen to be impersonated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.76,0:04:38.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, please
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.49,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So, the teachers came too
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:48.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The pros will meet the teachers firsthand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What impression do you think will make the students laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am bald so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bald...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd emphasize that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've actually made fun of it before
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So, more precisely, how could we play with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,When I enter the classroom
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I go like "How's everyone?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It also makes a nice sound
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you seem to be a really serious teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you ever laugh out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the funniest thing you last laughed with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:37.92,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And with that, Oota sensei, who can't remember the last time he laughed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has also been selected to be impersonated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:44.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanekatsu sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you have the "nice, nice!" catchphrase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When a student is doing well, I say like "nice, nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice, nice!". Oh, I think we can use this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanekatsu-sensei, and what about your dentures?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whenever I start shouting...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.24,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That is funny
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:14.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After gathering all the information about the teachers, the pros went back to TBS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.55,0:06:21.36,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They joined the other two pros who didn't participated before and held a meeting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.03,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we decide who has to wear make up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who can get the main roles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.01,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That looks so hard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:40.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Depending on the looks, voice tone and such, each pro was assigned a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:48.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kannatsuki will impersonate the eccentric Yamaguchi sensei, ex- member of a "poop seminar"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:54.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also, "bad diction" Oomori sensei, will be impersonated by Hori
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:07:01.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Mira will impersonate Ebara sensei, who can't stop saying "Who can try?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:07.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The serious but also good at dancing Oota sensei will be impersonated by Ehara
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:14.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And Mirakuru will be in charge of Nakayama sensei, who hisses after finishing her sentences
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:23.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Denture" Kanekatsu sensei and "Bald gag" Okuwaki sensei will also appear during the show
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:24.89,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Looks like a medley
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:28.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After deciding the roles, they start preparing the content
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.99,0:07:28.49,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like it to be realistic, like when I did it as a student
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, staying true to the character, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like us to do our best without distorting the characters too much
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.17,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Since his personality is so strong, he should appear at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, after a while
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And how should we introduce the teacher's catchphrases?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When Mirakuru appears, she would go like "suuuh",
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and a fart cushion will be heard in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the catchphrase lose power?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never prepared anything like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:11.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In order to "To make the students die of laughter",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.70,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's so tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They are serious about it and the preparation goes on until late at night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,On the next day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:22.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They get together once more and start rehearsing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They keep improving the content's quality
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:30.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And they finally wrapped it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If they went like "woow",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The reaction that impersonators hate the most
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Like "Ooooh"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.56,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If they don't laugh, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make them not go "oooh"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make them have fun
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:51.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The clueless students are gathered in the multi-purpose hall
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,These days you've all been slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you're all here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a teacher that has something to say to all of you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had it with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:09.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The students, after being fooled to believe they were being scolded, will meet the impersonators!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want every teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a few words
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,with all of you here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.77,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You can cut the air with a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:34.49,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After the unexpected appearance, they still don't know what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.12,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It was like: "what's going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, this guy looks a lot like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, who are YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'M YAMAGUCHI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.46,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really are Yamaguchi, tell me. You were in a seminar back in college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Which seminar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Turd seminar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A turd seminar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.51,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Yamaguchi has eaten bugs right? Which insect did you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A stink bug
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.31,0:09:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A stink bug!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:04.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After realizing what's going on... they burst out laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:03.30,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.46,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They find it hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:06.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many other teachers that are also angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oomori sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.92,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,The resemblance is amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:22.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They achieved an amazing resemblance
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the pinky, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I want you to remember the important things needed for a flower to blossom
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one, two and three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sensei, that's weird... It's pretty strange
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stamen and pistil... Please remember that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that, I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.66,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They find it hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your diction is terrible, so we have no idea what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My dihsshion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.37,0:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea what you say when you get mad
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there a teacher with a better diction in this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,WOW, WOW
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:11.42,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're going "WOW"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.24,0:11:16.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They really look alike
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So the other day we left it at page twentyfiiiiiiive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We will continuuuuue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:27.88,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.54,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:30.60,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They really are
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a one line joke
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When comparing "the other"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:34.86,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're laughing their heads off
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When comparing "the other" to..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.18,0:11:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,... "the othersssh"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:44.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:50.06,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:55.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,They started laughing right after the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:58.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What about the real person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:05.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In spite of the circumstances, he remains expressionless
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's never laughed in his life
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your right hand, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.46,0:12:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mouth? That's a duck face
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The contrast is hilarious
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dance now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:40.06,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Apparently he dances for the school festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:40.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the last one to make entrance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They're really similar
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:49.10,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.15,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Today I'd like to talk about my favourite team: Nippon Ham
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssss...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot, dot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of dots!! Too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dot dot dotdotdotdot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ssssss
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who should we call next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we bring Okuwaki sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Baldiewaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:36.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And finally they will go for Kanekatsu sensei's motto: "Nice, nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about the whole show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... "nice, nice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice, nice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm better at nicenicing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious I'm better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I AM BETTER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm "nice,nice"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone should decide who's the "nice, nicest"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.26,0:13:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you, come here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, how was our impersonations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nice, nice"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:09.66,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:18.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And like that, the impersonation show achieves a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised at the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You might've thought "What's going on?" or something
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was the closest to the original?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oota sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.42,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They're dying from laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.19,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They're literally dying from laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.43,0:14:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because you're happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why??
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you are overflowed with joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he's just overflowed with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The funniest thing was that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakayama sensei's impersonation was on point
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And Egara sensei too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They really got her essence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so funny that I'll probably won't be able to stop laughing during the next class
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.34,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.90,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They'll sure laugh during the next class
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the funniest thing I've ever seen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.26,0:15:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really moving...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel like really we accomplished?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I really do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,First time feeling like this
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The best in 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we did really well
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.84,0:15:26.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Students
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And also
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:30.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The impersonators
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone was filled with joy and laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It surely was a great day
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:42.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In a few words: it was an unexpectedly a heart-warming show
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.46,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That was something
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They found it hilarious didn't they
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Even one student was crying in the end
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He actually was
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:53.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He was crying so much that his hands were SOAKED
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:56.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The back of his hand was soaked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.54,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is that really possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.68,0:16:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They were confused in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:05.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, the atmosphere was quite intense
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:10.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Can't you participate in school festivals or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In schools, companies, and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:15.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.62,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It seems you can do it in another occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But the preparation is difficult as HELL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:28.50,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's good to have such a moving show, since the BPO is after us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,HEY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.86,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They're not after us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:35.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,OK, let's continue! Here comes our next presenter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellooo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.85,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Kaminari!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.30,0:16:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our first appearance so let us introduce ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Takumi Ishida, member of Kaminari
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Manabu Takeuchi, member of Kaminari
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to say something stupid!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but hitting him
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing to watch it live
