Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.02,0:26:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, truth be told
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.62,0:26:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I've noticed I'm actually better at Senryu poetry
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,than I am at Death Match
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.59,0:26:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, that's cool
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.56,0:26:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, could you give us a poem about being reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.83,0:27:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.73,0:27:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.10,0:27:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are called reckless
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.94,0:27:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd very much hate the fear of pain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but until you see your grandchild, you don't want to die
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.71,0:27:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.55,0:27:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be true
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.65,0:27:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be the real intention
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.85,0:27:24.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,His back is astounding
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.89,0:27:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.46,0:27:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there were too many characters
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.50,0:27:33.63,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,So scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.70,0:27:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, up next, try one about ambulances
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.83,0:27:36.57,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Look at the scars on his chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.10,0:27:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.77,0:27:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.24,0:27:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Another member complains
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.87,0:27:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes, exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.01,0:27:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambulances readily go back
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.18,0:27:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but that is just a common misconception
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.08,0:27:53.65,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He pulled it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.45,0:27:56.69,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He carries a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.19,0:27:56.69,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He's keeps pulling things out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.26,0:28:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, you were too short!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.02,0:28:01.32,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Wow, that was actually weak
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:05.56,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.23,0:28:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, next
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.86,0:28:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,try one about blood-shed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.07,0:28:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.37,0:28:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No longer worried when you're at a hospital with 5 stitches
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.87,0:28:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.84,0:28:19.71,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.28,0:28:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a proper 5-7-5 poem
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.35,0:28:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected for Senryu poetry
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.22,0:28:27.25,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Scary scary
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.08,0:28:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,(Can't be shown due to Compliance Programming)
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.35,0:28:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep telling me my poetry's off, let's see you give an example
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.56,0:28:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.99,0:28:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"The feelings of a parent whose child came to watch a match"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.03,0:28:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.07,0:28:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood is dripping
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.80,0:28:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,wondering if they'll be okay
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.71,0:28:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.71,0:28:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do it, I'll be fired
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.48,0:28:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, this too is wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.12,0:29:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Painful memories
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.79,0:29:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,will be born however
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.69,0:29:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this too is also wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.56,0:29:07.56,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.73,0:29:11.76,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Very high up
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.86,0:29:11.96,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.50,0:29:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,AARGH
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.00,0:29:22.77,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,All you could hear were shrieks
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.31,0:29:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I could do a 5-7-5 with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.88,0:29:32.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,When the retort is too strong, it puts people off instead
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:34.35,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Exactly as expected
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.35,0:29:36.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's no good if you go too strong
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.09,0:29:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Too strong of an reaction is unpleasant
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.82,0:29:38.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You were totally horror-struck
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.92,0:29:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.32,0:29:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who brought forth this theory shouldn't be afraid
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.06,0:29:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you saw it live, it's just as bad
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.33,0:29:47.33,Hamada,,0,0,0,,From a female point of view, how did you think of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.33,0:29:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My hands were sweating and I was getting goosebumps
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.93,0:29:53.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They were also swearing like hell
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.43,0:29:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so extreme, didn't real blood start to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.14,0:29:58.11,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But even with me normally, having Hamada as the serious role, I've had blood come out before
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.91,0:30:00.81,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,We were doing a sketch about detectives
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.02,0:30:03.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And he was supposed to interrogate me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.05,0:30:06.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,so he's like: "Spit it out!" and I'm like: "No way"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.00,0:30:10.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There was a pen on the table, and he grabbed me like this and went
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.14,0:30:12.05,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,BANG onto the table
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.05,0:30:14.37,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,and the pen went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.77,0:30:17.51,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Blood was dripping out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:20.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,and obviously, I spat it out
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.97,0:30:23.62,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Real quick
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.94,0:30:25.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.91,0:30:29.25,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will introduce more theories around the world, and verify them
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.25,0:30:31.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here on Viewers' Theory Corner
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:33.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Tonight's presenter is..
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.11,0:30:39.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Koyabu Kazutoyo
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.40,0:30:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a quick verification I did the other day
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.85,0:30:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"Otsukare-sama deshita"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.57,0:30:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The theory that if the "O" and "shita" are present
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything could go in between
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.28,0:30:52.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.51,0:30:52.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I remember that
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.40,0:30:54.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That is indeed the case
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.40,0:30:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time, an everyday occurrence
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.54,0:31:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I bring you, "When you hear it, but don't notice it" Series, Part 2
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.28,0:31:01.45,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.45,0:31:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.45,0:31:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The theory of restaurant music: Changing the lyrics of famous songs
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.54,0:31:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and seeing if anyone will notice
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.82,0:31:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see if this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.28,0:31:16.42,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It'd probably depend on how you do it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.42,0:31:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If they didn't know the song, they might think those are the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,For the songs, if they only know the first couplet
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.74,0:31:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they might think that they just don't know the rest of it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:26.94,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.94,0:31:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've tested the theory. Please watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.42,0:31:37.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Verifying: Theory of not noticing the different lyrics to famous songs being played inside restaurants
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.02,0:31:39.02,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.02,0:31:43.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This time, the research has been conducted at this cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.00,0:31:46.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The first song is..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.20,0:31:52.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Tube's song
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.42,0:31:51.22,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Great song
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.45,0:31:53.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,"Ah~ Summer Holidays"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.40,0:31:57.97,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.28,0:31:55.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's change around the singers
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.40,0:31:59.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The singer for the changed song not only has similar appearances
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.05,0:32:02.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but also his voice is very similar, Bu-Tube
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.28,0:32:03.97,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's an imitation
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.57,0:32:08.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The targets are these three people, where the fake song was played on different days
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.88,0:32:06.85,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,They don't seem motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.85,0:32:09.94,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Fujimoto is quite sensitive these kinds of small changes
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.14,0:32:12.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,During the time they are waiting on their order
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.91,0:32:13.80,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling Hashimoto wouldn't get this wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.57,0:32:15.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the song with changed lyrics was played
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.74,0:32:27.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Will we see if they have noticed the changes made in the lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.62,0:32:26.91,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chris will know this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.91,0:32:28.77,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chris knows a lot about this song
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.77,0:32:31.25,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chris likes this song
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.02,0:32:45.28,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,If you listen to it often, you'd be fine
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.28,0:32:47.28,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,like this guy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.14,0:32:50.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The very similar imitation to the song
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.00,0:32:55.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has left these three clueless that it is a different singer
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.11,0:32:56.71,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.71,0:32:58.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Eventually down the line
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.57,0:33:01.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,small changes are made to the lyrics
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.94,0:33:03.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First is Level 1
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.94,0:33:08.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The hit line "Ah, Summer Holidays" is changed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.74,0:33:06.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Eh, they're changing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.22,0:33:08.14,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I would notice it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.51,0:33:11.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,What is the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.28,0:33:12.08,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Isn't that risky?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.08,0:33:13.91,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Is this only Level 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.20,0:33:15.17,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Isn't it too obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:23.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah I see
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.65,0:33:23.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.57,0:33:26.48,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, like that way
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:30.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected, the subtle change to the lyrics has gone through the three
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.25,0:33:33.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next up is Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.97,0:33:38.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The second lyrics are still related to summer, but are totally different
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.71,0:33:56.74,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.68,0:34:01.42,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Using those kinds of summer words
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.94,0:34:04.65,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah? No way
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.00,0:34:09.08,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's not weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.16,0:34:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472.5,544)}Whose cover is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.90,0:34:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(699,680)}Whose cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.00,0:34:15.00,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,That's impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.62,0:34:17.42,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to tell
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.40,0:34:24.91,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,"Whose cover?" he said
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.51,0:34:28.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we see that he has noticed it's not the actual artist
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.11,0:34:32.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The remaining two people aren't particularly showing any reaction
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.48,0:34:28.94,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Ah, incredible
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.54,0:34:29.20,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It is
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.11,0:34:36.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now onto the final level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.22,0:34:39.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The chorus of the song will be entirely Winter-based
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.94,0:34:42.05,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It'll be noticed this time
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.02,0:34:57.00,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Chris already knows
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.67,0:34:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,690)}This isn't it, {\alpha&HFF&}if it's not Maeda, I don't feel motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.47,0:34:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,690)}This isn't it, if it's not Maeda, {\alpha&HFF&}I don't feel motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.24,0:34:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,690)}This isn't it, if it's not Maeda, I don't feel motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.42,0:35:02.54,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:08.25,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He hasn't moved at all
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.65,0:35:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,692)}This is {\alpha&HFF&}one of those parody songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.09,0:35:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,692)}This is one of those {\alpha&HFF&}parody songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.09,0:35:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,692)}This is one of those parody songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:14.85,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.53,0:35:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,692)} I'm pretty sure {\alpha&HFF&}he never said "New Year"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.63,0:35:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,692)} I'm pretty sure he never said "New Year"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.34,0:35:19.82,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,He knew too much
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.25,0:35:19.82,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.82,0:35:22.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Now all will be revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.77,0:35:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Wednesday Downtown
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.82,0:35:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you put in this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.37,0:35:28.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Nothing's in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.68,0:35:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he suspicious about the drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.31,0:35:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I not notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.62,0:35:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the song "Ah Summer Holidays"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.54,0:35:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for the original singer, Maeda
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.20,0:35:42.00,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.00,0:35:42.00,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,I apologise
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.11,0:35:44.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We also reveal it to the two people who didn't react
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.76,0:35:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(711,712)}It's about cold
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.42,0:35:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the original, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.28,0:36:00.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As expected, he didn't notice anything at all
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.17,0:36:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that my first time on Wednesday Downtown would be this way
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.94,0:36:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize ..
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.45,0:36:11.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,However, with Fujimoto
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.97,0:36:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed it
