Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.59,0:40:17.26,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Is that what you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.26,0:40:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can definitely hold it in
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.10,0:40:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can even hold it for two hours
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.20,0:40:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought there'd be a better one but you totally missed it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.40,0:40:27.97,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Okay you've got her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.97,0:40:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is feeling powerless holding in your pee!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.97,0:40:29.87,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He's locked on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.07,0:40:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it a bit! You ain't gonna get paid just sitting on your ass cuz you got a pretty face you idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.61,0:40:36.35,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So sorry for you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.35,0:40:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel grateful for your parents and grandparents
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.88,0:40:40.75,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,His emotion are a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.75,0:40:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I bring you this theory based on that
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.29,0:40:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The theory of being helpless when you're carrying a urine sample
